" The Cisco Umbrella module for the AnyConnect Secure Mobility Client for Android is an extension for the AnyConnect client that provides DNS-layer protection for Android v6.0.1 and later, and can be enabled with or without an AnyConnect license.

It blocks users from visiting websites associated with phishing, crypto mining, ransomware and other malware. Admins can also enforce domain level content filtering by category, and get device-level visibility and reporting.

For more information, please reach out to umbrella-support@cisco.com. Use of Cisco Umbrella is governed by the Universal Cloud Agreement.
